reviewText: I grew up watching this tape and still love the cartoons! Some of the best one's in my opinion are "Somewhere in Dreamland" (1936), "Christmas Comes but Once a Year" (1936), and "Jack Frost" (1934). You can look these up on YouTube as well. These are all old cartoons, but that makes it unique and a special VHS to keep in the collection of Christmas movies. I only wish that it was on DVD now.

I would love to give you a review if you would at least list the titles of the cartoons so I would know whether to buy it or not, and then I could give you a review!
Very truly yours,
Marty
